fields.title: Software Development
fields.overview: This module introduces programming concepts and structures using a problem-based learning approach. The fundamentals of a programming language are covered to facilitate the student analysing a problem and then designing and implementing a suitable solution. The development life-cycle from analysis, design, implementation, debugging and version control are covered to ensure the student understands and is able to demonstrate the process.
